Class SQLServerFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.DAO.AbstractDAOFactory
      • server.DAO.SQLServerFactory

  • public class SQLServerFactory
extends AbstractDAOFactory
    Ths class creates an SQLServer factory It contains all the DAO used in the project, and provides ways to get access to it.
